tooltip.eternal_starlight.aethersent_arm: When wearing full set: Summons meteors over enemy's head when hurt
tooltip.eternal_starlight.thermal_spring: When wearing: Ignites enemies that damage you, reduces the amount of fire damage you take
tooltip.eternal_starlight.glacite_armor: When wearing: Freezes enemies that damage you, make you immune to freeze damage
tooltip.eternal_starlight.swamp_silver_a: When wearing full set: Immune to any negative effects
advancements.eternal_starlight.obtain_st: After obtaining the starlight flower, why not use it to make a bowl of soup?
advancements.eternal_starlight.obtain_sw: From the mud, but not stained
advancements.eternal_starlight.obtain_se: Craft a seeking eye using an ender pearl and eight starlight flowers
advancements.eternal_starlight.kill_gole: Find the Golem Forge with redstone dust and seeking eye, and defeat the Starlight Golem
advancements.eternal_starlight.obtain_th: Obtaining thermal springtone. Tips: Only flames can destroy giant plants that live in this dimension...
advancements.eternal_starlight.kill_luna: Find the Cursed Garden with crystal moss carpets and seeking eye, and defeat the giant Lunar Monstrosity
advancements.eternal_starlight.use_bloss: Swinging in the boundless Milky Way

message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_giv: Take this. You can open the portal with it. Be careful not to loose it!
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_hel: Hello, adventurer! What can I do for you?
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_kil: Hello, warrior! What can I do for you?
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_bye: Bye then. Have a nice day!
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_ask: What is that structure behind you?
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_por:
Well... That's what I've benn guarding here for years.
It's a portal to a mysterious and magical place.
Only the brave ones can pass this portal.
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_pro: Then I'd like to prove myself!
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_pra: As far as I know, you've already killed the ender dragon. So let me guide you into the portal. Here! Take this.
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_fig:
If you want to prove yourself, fighting with me is the only way...
I sincerely don't recommend you to do so. But you have the right to decide.
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_acc: Let's fight! I'm very sure that I'll be the winner!
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_den: Well, I agree with you. Maybe I should go somewhere else.
message.eternal_starlight.gatekeeper_fun: That's fun to know! I'm leaving now. Goodbye!
message.eternal_starlight.dream_catcher_: If you fall, get knocked down, pick yourself up off the ground...
